data.description: Charming move in ready small ranch home. Recently updated with granite countertops, all new doors and hardware, all new trim, all new luxury vinyl floor throught-out the home, also completely remodeled bathroom from top to bottom.  All walls and ceilings freshly painted as well as exterior painting along with all new window treatments.  Schedule a showing and come see this charming home.
